<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Your Trial is Ending Soon</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}

  <div style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color: #f0ad4e;">Your Trial is Ending Soon</h1>

    <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

    <p>We wanted to let you know that your free trial will end on <strong>{{trialEndDate}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>To continue using all features without interruption, please upgrade to a paid plan before your trial expires.</p>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f0ad4e;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>What happens when your trial ends?</strong></p>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Your access to premium features will be disabled</li>
        <li>Your data will be preserved for 30 days</li>
        <li>You can upgrade at any time to restore access</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    {{#if upgradeUrl}}
    <p style="margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{upgradeUrl}}" style="background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
        Upgrade Now
      </a>
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Thank you for trying our service!
    </p>

    <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 40px;">
      If you have any questions about upgrading, please contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
